## URL Shortening Program ##

This application is a programming task that I had at an interview. My original execution and interview ended in disaster, but I am a trooper who learns from my mistakes.
I will take this application and turn it into something that I can use for later and can demonstrate it for future interviews.

The goal of this application is to take a URL and shorten it, then store that shortened URL in a database store for use later.
The application should handle many users at once. It should also cleanse the database whenever an item becomes too old.

